<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA36">
<l>kaiya kaṉalāḻik kārkkaṭalvāy veṇcaṅkam</l>
<l>veyya kataicārṅkam veñcuṭarvāḷ – ceyya</l>
<l>paṭaiparavai pāḻi paṉinī rulaka</l>
<l>maṭiyaḷanta māya ṉavaṟku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In [his] hands – the fiery discus, the white conch from the cloud[-coloured] sea,</l>
<l>the cruel club, the Śārṅga bow, the hotly glowing sword</l>
<l>– weapons red [from blood are] the Dark one’s who with [his] foot measured</l>
<l>the world [surrounded] by the chilly water, the surface [of the ocean his] place.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
